<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_4383218e-2ecf-4e1f-b160-18f336d6e45d" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>J5D2</sptc><title id="_3ca5f97f-6cb1-4228-8d78-3180423bcc5b">Application of Part</title><archive-num/><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/7903_0.3.0.xml" variation="NSW" variation-type="REPLACE">NSW REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_08a787ac-7622-47cb-a40a-32d442229fdb" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_8e90fe41-e843-4704-8e75-37e25445b8fc">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1236_1.0.0.xml#_2f02788f-8757-4689-b36e-e44d96524cc9" id="_5699436e-3b3a-40ab-baa9-f64197143def" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">Deemed-to-Satisfy Provisions</xref> of this Part apply to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_4286859f-ca89-4faf-8c12-87964566c19d">elements forming the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1259_5.7.0.xml#_71ea06f9-79ec-4eae-bdf4-d90302f51eb5" id="_9557a585-a49c-44a5-8154-17c507df3ea6" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">envelope</xref> of a Class 3, 5, 6, 7, 8 or 9 building; and</li><li id="_aa8025fb-9a96-4435-81c5-d8d36af18d0b">the external building <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1269_0.5.0.xml#_13553d4f-118c-47e2-90ba-9892194abdf6" id="_43487dbb-65de-47ea-a208-ea01def65dea" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">fabric</xref> of a Class 4 part of a building.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_e61a3307-2a50-48a4-b0f0-5f20de2f54e0" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_47a07096-4d28-43c4-a55e-f58005c1af28">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Notwithstanding (1), the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1236_1.0.0.xml#_2f02788f-8757-4689-b36e-e44d96524cc9" id="_748bd6a7-2f10-4b50-accb-dfced2efa901" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Deemed-to-Satisfy Provisions</xref> of this Part do not apply to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_617eac1d-7ea6-4734-ac2f-f960f51629f4">a building in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_96f4d10f-0c6d-4672-af4b-33741a3f63dc" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 1, 2, 3 or 5 where the only means of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_75a61a01-0a96-4371-8a1e-7c76ab9c8e8a" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> is by using an evaporative cooler; or</li><li id="_d5a36474-c0c0-4ea3-8634-8d2b652d3c30">a permanent building opening, in a space where a gas appliance is located, that is necessary for the safe operation of a gas appliance; or</li><li id="_eb3bd263-7ed5-490f-9f50-f98548d77e59">a building or space where the mechanical ventilation <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_c4254586-eea0-44cc-a9a5-8a20a9dfd22c" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/57_0.9.0.xml#_a2a7a658-2b2e-4234-bc6b-f424abbfba1c" id="_a762c0ed-5686-4dff-9bcb-cdf034a81463" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-part">Part F6</xref> provides sufficient pressurisation to prevent infiltration.</li></ol></subclause></clause>